"""
SPR.py
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Utility to load the SPR_BENCH benchmark datasets
Using HuggingFace’s `datasets` library.

Directory layout expected
SPR_BENCH/
 ├─ train.csv   (20000 rows)
