\section{Additional Ablations and Figures}
Figures for ablation studies (removing the L1 penalty, removing the bag-of-characters, and freezing character embeddings) are included here. They show similar trends of rapid training convergence with a plateau in validation scores. These experiments confirm that absolute performance remains near 0.80 on test F1 under varied training configurations.

\begin{figure}[h!]
